\id JAS ZYA- Bible Iyansi
\h ZYAK
\toc1 Un'kaan a Zyak
\toc2 ZYAK
\toc3 Zya
\mt2 Un'kaan a
\mt1 Zyak
\imt1 Nsɛmà
\ip Un'kaan a Zyak we anà un'lwaaŋ a nswɛɛŋ mwɛy bàpɛ « akà iköŋ a baan a Nzam bàpää u mɛɛn. » Zyak kan'sɔn akà aklistɔ ntɔn muswaŋ nkääl a ube aba ba a ba anà baar mpa abà Ayudà.
\ip Itiir a ndaa abyà uboo byimwɛy ungö a imwɛy ukɔɔn alab un'lwaaŋ aŋàbwaŋ. Zyak wàmutɛn utàtwɛb ndaa iler an'yeerà: ma màfàfà akà Nzam anà ma bàfàlɔm akà nde unsà làkwikilà lanswà. Unsà ya yanswà, an'lwɛŋ amà mà ntɔn làmbwà anà un'naaŋ, nsii anà ndɛb, an'lɔɔŋ aŋàbwaŋ mà Nzam u mbwo isal. Un'söön a un'kaan awà wàmutɛn unsà muküünà ntɔn un'kɔl aŋàyɔŋ awà uboo a Ikööŋ. Ungö, nde wàmuswaŋ isin a ndaa akyà ban'kwo baar muyöb unsà un'kaan ande awà asànaa: un'tüüb awà uboo a làkwikilà anà isal. Uboo a itiir a ndaa a ifà ifà, nde wàmuswaŋ ube ufàkyer làlem. Ungö, nde wàmuswaŋ an'yeerà a ndandaa uboo a isin a ndaa. Nde wà munyääŋà unsà muküünà baar bàfàtwaal an'sye, anà bàfàkyey uyɔl ntɔn mutsüül atɔŋ aba nsaŋ, anà nde wàmutɛn unsà muküünà ntɔn aŋun'naaŋ, ntɔn an'kyeey bàfàmɛɛy ba baar a isal aba. Mumay, nde wàmuswaŋ nkääŋ a mpem, ngyamàkà, muküünà.
\ip Ndɔ̈ɔ̈m kan'sà un'kaan awà akà aklistɔ yuleŋ: kà mukyey Làsaŋ Aŋàbwaŋ là Yɛsu anki, wɛɛ làkwikilà làmɛnà mbwo asin. Ntɔn, « làkwikilà làkɔ̈ɔ̈n isal làŋàkwà. »
\c 1
\s1 Mbɔr
\p 
\v 1 Mɛ Zyak, un'syääl a Nzam anà Mwol Yɛsu Klistɔ, an'pà mbɔr akà in'sɛŋ myàkwem aŋiyweel myàpää u mɛɛn manswà.
\s1 Mpay anà làkyän
\p 
\v 2 Atɔŋ amɛ, làwɛl unsà mpem aŋàbwaŋ nsii yanswà ifàlayeel,
\v 3 ntɔn bɛ làkyàyöb, isàkal naa làkwikilà abɛ làngwal kusà a nsii, nsii ayi ifàlabuul bàŋàtsim mbɔɔn.
\v 4 Wɛɛ, wɛy naa muküünà abɛ usyäl ubwaŋàbwaŋ, ntɔn bɛ làkäl bàŋàmaay anà bàŋàkwo, ukɔɔn too.
\p 
\v 5 Isàkal naa umwɛy uboo a bɛ an'yeerà matɛy, wɛy nde ulɔ̈m ma akà Nzam awà afàpà akà baar banswà u mpem aŋàbwaŋ ukɔɔn an'pɛl.
\v 6 Wɛɛ, wɛy nde ulɔ̈m anà làkwikilà, ukɔɔn asà nkyɛɛr. Ntɔn mbuur afàsà nkyɛɛr wà asànaa ibɔ a an'dà a ngyäl ufàsɛn un'pöb.
\v 7 Mbuur a tub awà twon kan'si naa nde asàwal undiir akà Mwol,
\v 8 ntɔn nde wà bölà a bölà anà we amà an'kyän mɔ̈ɔ̈l unsà ndaa ande yanswà.
\p 
\v 9 Wɛy un'tɔŋ awà ŋàlàmbwà umɛn un'sak umpal kun'sɛɛn Nzam,
\v 10 anà ŋun'naaŋ umɛn un'sak umpal kun'tyeey Nzam, ntɔn nde asàlyaaŋ asànaa iful a an'ywaŋ.
\v 11 Ntɔn taaŋ lan'yàsɛnà anà ipar a mbaa a mwäänà ande, kyan'kuuŋ kite, iful akya kyan'bwà, anà ubwaŋ a kya ban'wà. Mbwo mwɛy sye usàkal ŋun'naaŋ unsà isal ande.
\p 
\v 12 Un'sak akà mbuur afànwaan unsà nsii, ntɔn, isàkal naa nde kan'böŋ, nde asàwal mpà a mɔ̈ɔ̈ ayà bàbön mupà akà baar Bàfun'kwen.
\s1 Nzam anà nsii
\p 
\v 13 Mbuur twon kan'tɛn, isàkal naa nde kan'bwà unsà ndɛb, naa: « Ndɛb amɛ yi yan'fà akà Nzam ». Ntɔn Nzam ukwe anki naa ube bun'lwɛb, anà nde ŋakwo ufàlwab anki mbuur.
\v 14 Mbuur mbuur afàbwà u ndɛb a ngyööm a mpem ande ŋakwo, waa ya yun'syen anà yun'bwiy.
\v 15 Ngyööm a mpem isàpfɛy, ya ifàbɔr man'be. Man'be màsàyɛl, ma màfàbɔr ukwà.
\p 
\v 16 Atɔŋ amɛ bànkwen, twon lan'bwà ndwaŋ:
\v 17 kab a ntal lanswà anà kab aŋàkwo lanswà màfàfà du, akà Taa a pɛɛlà. Amu nde nsɔɔmà yatɛy, itàkal naa taaŋ lan'nwaan anà nsöŋ.
\v 18 Nde ŋakwo kàkwen mukipà mɔ̈ɔ̈ u mbwo a ndaa ande yàndandaa, ntɔn bi ikäl bàtàtwɛb unsà ikyeer ande byanswà.
\s1 Ngweem anà nsyääl a Ndaa a Nzam
\p 
\v 19 Atɔŋ amɛ bànkwen, bɛ làkyàyɔb naa bɛ làbà aŋun'yɛnà. Wɛy naa akà mbuur mwɛy ukɔ̈ɔ̈n akal anà ulɛy muwem, wɛɛ nde ukäl anà ulɛy mutɛn anà muwem nkyɛl,
\v 20 ntɔn nkyɛl a mbuur ifàkyer anki balàbal a Nzam.
\v 21 Kyakin, làpiy làbiin lanswà anà un'fur a nkyɛl, làwɛl unsà làbɔ̈ɔ̈n lanswà ndaa a Nzam bàkön u mpem abɛ, ntɔn ya yan'kwo mukàlatswà mɔ̈ɔ̈.
\p 
\v 22 Wɛɛ làsyääl ndaa, kà nà muwem ya mpɛl anki, naa tɛy bɛ làbàmukur bɛ ŋakwo.
\v 23 Kyakin, isàkal naa mbuur kan'wem ndaa a Nzam, wɛɛ nde ya usyääl anki, nde wà asànaa mbuur akalerà unsà làman anà kan'man ntabwey ande asànaa awà nde.
\v 24 Ungö kan'may nde muler, nde kan'kyà anà abwà adiimà naa nde kàkäl aben.
\v 25 Wɛɛ mbuur afàsà mii ande ubwaŋàbwaŋ unsà Un'kɔɔn aŋàkwo, Un'kɔɔn a insaay, anà afàsyääl wa, kà nà uwem wa mpɛl anki, wɛɛ usyääl wa, mbuur awun asàkal mbuur a un'sak unsà ndaa usàkyer nde.
\p 
\v 26 Isàkal naa mbuur mwɛy afàsi naa nde we anà inzaam, wɛɛ nde ufàkyekyekà anki ntɛɛn ande, nde afàkur mpem ande ŋakwo: inzaam ande kyà bunàbun.
\v 27 Inzaam a ndandaa anà ikɔ̈ɔ̈n too u mii a Taa Nzam aki: ubay itii anà akweel adim unsà mpay aba, anà mukal unsà igyɛɛŋ ntɔn mukɔɔn abwà unsà làbiin a mɛɛn mà.
\c 2
\s1 Un'kɔl aŋàyↄŋ
\p 
\v 1 Atɔŋ amɛ, bɛ baar làbye anà làkwikilà amu Mwol abi wàlàkoo, Yɛsu Klistɔ, twon lan'kal anà un'kɔl aŋayɔŋ.
\v 2 Abun, bi itàsi naa mbuur mwɛy kan'yàbilà uboo a nköŋ abɛ, nde kan'bwaar mpɛr a wɔl anà ipfɛy aŋàbwaŋ, anà isàkal sye naa ŋàlàmbwà mwɛy kan'bwaar ipfɛy a mbiin kan'yàbilà,
\v 3 isàkal naa bɛ lan'düül muwal mbuur kan'bwaar ipfɛy aŋàbwaŋ, anà lan'tɛn a nde naa: « Ngye, bwaay pà kà ikal aŋàbwaŋ ki », wɛɛ akà ŋàlàmbwà, bɛ lan'tɛn naa: « Ngye, kyen kakäl umbär kunà. » Mbalà yumwɛy naa: « Kyen kaswen kunà kà ikal in'fàsà mɛ in'kɔl. »
\v 4 Nkye abun bɛ kà un'kɔl aŋàyↄŋ lan'kyer anki? Nkye bɛ kà làbà ambak a kɔɔrà anki?
\p 
\v 5 Atɔŋ amɛ bànkwen, làwem: nkye aŋàlàmbwà kà Nzam kasɔ̈ɔ̈l anki u mii a baar ntɔn mukabuul aŋin'naaŋ unsà làkwikilà anà muwal kwal a Imwol akyà kàpɛ nde ilää mupà akà baar bàfun'kwen?
\v 6 Wɛɛ bɛ, bɛ làduum làkoo a aŋàlàmbwà. Nkye kà ŋin'naaŋ anki bàfàlapà mpay? Nkye kà ba anki sye bàfàlasyen u làbay a nsaŋ?
\v 7 Nkye kà ba anki bàfàbɛy ikↄb a ntwɛn bàfàbel udu a bɛ?
\p 
\v 8 Inye, isàkal naa bɛ làfàlab kiin a Un'kɔɔn, asànaa itɛɛnà Ndaa Aŋàsɔn naa: « Ngye asàkwen mbääb angye asànaa ngye ŋakwo », bɛ làfàkyer ubwaŋ.
\v 9 Wɛɛ isàkal naa bɛ làfàkyer un'kɔl aŋàyↄŋ, bɛ làfàkyer man'be, anà Un'kɔɔn afàlatsüül mbar ntɔn bɛ làfàbɛy wa.
\v 10 Ntɔn, isàkal naa mbuur mwɛy afàlab Un'kɔɔn wanswà, wɛɛ nde afàbɛy ikal imwɛy, apan nde afàbɛy wa wanswà.
\v 11 Ntɔn, Nzam kàtɛn naa: « Twon an'tà inswem », nde sye kàtɛn naa: « Twon an'dwa ». Isàkal naa ngye atɛ anki inswem, wɛɛ ngye an'dwa mbuur, yöb naa ngye an'bɛy Un'kɔɔn.
\v 12 Làtɛn anà làkyer asànaa baar bàfatsüül nsaŋ aba u mbwo a un'kɔɔn afàpà insaay.
\v 13 Ntɔn, Nzam usàwem anki ngyɛb mpal usàtsul nde nsaŋ a mbuur mpa afàwem baar bumwɛy ngyɛb. Wɛɛ ngyɛb ifàwal iböŋ u ntsüül a nsaŋ.
\s1 Làkwikilà anà isal
\p 
\v 14 Atɔŋ amɛ, ndöŋ nà mbuur mutɛn naa: « Mɛ in'we anà làkwikilà », isàkal naa nde isal byatɛy? Nkye làkwikilà alà lan'kwo lun'tsü mɔ̈ɔ̈?
\v 15 Bi itàwal naa un'tɔŋ mwɛy wàbaal itàkal wun'kaar, kà we anà undiir a bwaar itàkal wàdyà anki ilä byanswà,
\v 16 wɛɛ umwɛy uboo a bɛ utɛn a nde naa: « Kyen unsà duu, bwaar ipfɛy a mpye anà dyà ubwaŋàbwaŋ », wɛɛ nde akà undiir mwɛy kun'pɛ anki ntɔn ndür ande, apan ndöŋ nà?
\v 17 Ya yà abwɛy sye ntɔn làkwikilà: isàkal naa la lan'kɔɔn isal, la là undiir aŋàkwà la ŋakwo.
\p 
\v 18 Wɛɛ mbuur mwɛy asàtɛn naa: « Ngye, ngye awe anà làkwikilà, wɛɛ mɛ, mɛ in'we anà isal! Nswɛŋ làkwikilà angye làkɔ̈ɔ̈n isal! Wɛɛ akà mɛ, mɛ in'sàswaŋ làkwikilà amɛ u mbwo a isal amɛ.
\v 19 Nkye ngye afàsà làkwikilà naa Nzam wà mwɛy? Yà ubwaŋ. In'sɔŋà sye myàfàsà làkwikilà anà myàkyer afàtɛɛr! »
\v 20 Insil a mbuur, nkye ngye akwen muyöb naa làkwikilà làkɔ̈ɔ̈n isal ndöŋ latɛy?
\v 21 Nkye taaràbi Abàlam bun'twey anki wàbalàbal u mbwo a isal ande, mpal kàkäb nde mwan ande Isak udu a mɛsà a ibɔɔn?
\v 22 Ngye an'man naa làkwikilà anà isal ande byan'kyà mbwo mwɛy: ntɔn isal ande, làkwikilà ande lan'mɛnà làŋàkwo.
\v 23 Abà, ndaa bàsön yi unsà Ndaa Aŋàsɔn yàkyer akwo: « Abàlam kàsi làkwikilà akà Nzam, waa Nzam kun'twey wàbalàbal. » Anà bun'beelà un'sam a Nzam.
\v 24 Bɛ lan'man naa mbuur an'kwo bun'twey wàbalàbal ntɔn isal, kà nà ntɔn làkwikilà mpɛl anki.
\p 
\v 25 Ya yàkäl abun sye ntɔn Rayab, un'kaar a pasàsɛ. Nkye kà ntɔn isal ande anki waa nde kàtoo wàbalàbal, ntɔn kàwɛl nde akyeey a Isàlɛl anà katwey nde mbwo asin?
\v 26 Asànaa ndür ikɔ̈ɔ̈n un'swey yàŋàkwà, abun sye, làkwikilà làkɔ̈ɔ̈n isal làŋàkwà.
\c 3
\s1 Làlem
\p 
\v 1 Atɔŋ amɛ, twon lan'kal bàmbɔɔn mulɔŋ. Bɛ làkyàyöb naa nsaŋ abi alɔɔŋ isàkal yà ngwal.
\v 2 Ntɔn bi banswà ifàtà an'pfürà. Isàkal naa mbuur mwɛy ufàtà anki pfürà unsà ntɛɛn ande, nde wà mbuur mwɛy wàŋàkwo anà wàŋàtsim muyaal ndür ande yanswà.
\v 3 Isàkal naa bi kan'bäm un'siŋ u mun a mpoonà ntɔn ya iläb ukwen a bi, bi kan'kwo sye iyaal ndür aya yanswà.
\v 4 Làler sye an'swà: itàkal naa ma mà uteer mbɔɔn, anà in'pöb a ngwal myàsiinà ma, kà indiir imwɛy kyan'swà bàfàbel naa kuvɛrnay laa isyen kya ma mper ukwen kaptɛn.
\v 5 Ifà imwɛy sye, làlem là kitiir a ndür imwɛy. Wɛɛ la lye anà uyɔl mutɛn ndaa akölàköl.
\p Làsii làmwɛy asànaa kimbaa ifàkuuŋ kya ndwaŋ a kölàköl!
\v 6 Làlem sye là mbaa. La là kiin a ube banswà. La là uboo a itiir a ndür abi anà làfàsà làbiin u ndür yanswà, làfàkuuŋ mɔ̈ɔ̈ abi wanswà. La ŋakwo sye làŋàkuŋà a mbaa a nsye a mbaa.
\v 7 Mbuur kan'kwo mukwaam ntsür a umpɔr, itàkal nɛn, itàkal ntäy, itàkal nsö.
\v 8 Wɛɛ akà mbuur mwɛy ukwe anki mukwaam làlem! La là bölà a bölà, là undiir mwɛy wà ube anà làŋàyɔl a idyà ifàtwaal ukwà.
\v 9 U mbwo a la, bi ifàsaak Mwol anà Taa. Anà u mbwo a la sye, bi ifàküül baar abà kàkyer Nzam kà ifà ande.
\v 10 Nsaak anà un'küül yàfàtoo mun nsil nà wa. Atɔŋ amɛ, ya ikwo anki mukal abà!
\v 11 Nkye ntwà a an'dà ifàtwey an'dà a ntsà anà màbuul mun nsil nà wa?
\v 12 Atɔŋ amɛ, nkye un'te a fige afàbɔr mbɛŋ a ɔlivɛ, itàkal un'te a vin nkye afàbɔr mbɛŋ a fige? Ifuunà a an'dà a muŋ ikwo anki sye itwey an'dà a ntsà.
\s1 An'yeerà màfàfà du
\p 
\v 13 Nà awe an'yeerà anà un'yɛnà uboo a bɛ? Wɛy naa nde uswɛŋ ma unsà nkääl anà làbɔ̈ɔ̈n anà an'yeerà ande.
\v 14 Wɛɛ, isàkal naa bɛ, bɛ làbà anà mpem aŋàyɔl a un'köl a buul anà dweelà a an'sye, twon lan'swaŋ ngaal, twon lan'pà ndandaa mpay u mbwo a loor abɛ.
\v 15 An'yeerà amà kà man'fà du anki, ma mà màmɛɛn, mà ntsür, min'sɔŋà.
\v 16 Ntɔn ikal akyà un'köl anà an'sye, an'pfürà anà ube bà ifà ifà byà paa sye.
\v 17 Wɛɛ an'yeerà a du màŋàtàpɔŋà, ungö mà duu, mà làbɔ̈ɔ̈n, mà un'tüüb, màŋàyɔl a ngyɛb anà mbɛŋ aŋàbwaŋ, mpa amye anà un'kɔl aŋàyↄŋ anà mpem yweel.
\v 18 Imbɛŋ a balàbal kyàŋàkɔn unsà duu akà baar bàfàkyer ndaa a duu.
\c 4
\s1 Làsin apà Nzam
\p 
\v 1 Nkir anà ngwiy uboo abɛ yan'fà ken? Nkye kà ntɔn ilään byàfànwaan uboo a ndür abɛ anki?
\v 2 Bɛ làfàyɔm mpem anà bɛ làfàwal anki undiir. Bɛ làbà adwää anà aŋun'köl, anà bɛ làkwe anki muwal iböŋ. Bɛ làfànwaan anà làfàtwal an'sye. Bɛ undiir watɛy, ntɔn bɛ làfàlɔm anki.
\v 3 Kya bɛ làsàlɔm, bɛ làfàwal anki undiir, ntɔn ndɔ̈ɔ̈m abɛ yà ube: ntɔn indiir làfàlɔm bɛ, bɛ bya làfàsyääl ntɔn ilään abɛ.
\v 4 Bɛ aŋinswem! Nkye bɛ làyöb anki naa ukwen a indiir a mɛɛn bà un'yiiŋ a Nzam? Abun, mbuur usàkwen mukal un'sam a mɛɛn, nde kan'bulà un'yiiŋ a Nzam.
\v 5 Nkye bɛ làsii naa abunàbun waa Ndaa Aŋàsɔn itɛɛnà naa: « Nzam akwen unsà un'köl Dweelà kàsi nde amu bi. »
\v 6 Wɛɛ Nzam afipà kab a ngway làŋàsöön, ntɔn Ndaa Aŋàsɔn itɛn naa: « Nzam afàmbäär aŋun'yɔl, wɛɛ nde afàswaŋ ubwaŋ ande akà aŋàlàbɔ̈ɔ̈n. »
\v 7 Abun, làpɛ mɔ̈ɔ̈ abɛ akà Nzam, wɛɛ làmbäär ileŋ, waa kya isàtiin ukwɛl apà bɛ.
\v 8 Làsin tsütsü apà Nzam, waa nde usàsin tsütsü apà bɛ. Bɛ baar a man'be, làywɛy an'kɔɔ abɛ, anà làpöŋ mpem abɛ, baar a mpem yweel!
\v 9 Làyweer mpay abɛ, làsi un'saabà anà làlel. Wɛy naa an'sɛ abɛ màbulà ilel anà un'sak abɛ ubulà ngyɛb!
\v 10 Làkäl anà làbɔ̈ɔ̈n kusà a Mwol waa nde usàlasɛɛn.
\s1 Twon an'tsül un'tɔŋ nsaŋ
\p 
\v 11 Atɔŋ, twon lan'twe bɛ a bɛ. Mbuur afàtwe un'tɔŋ ande, itàkal naa afàtsul nsaŋ ande, nde wàmusaal Un'kɔɔn anà mutsüül wa mbar. Kyekà isàkal naa ngye an'tsüül Un'kɔɔn mbar, ngye afàkal anki un'syääl a wa, wɛɛ ngye awà ntɛɛn.
\v 12 Mbuur mwɛy mpɛl afàpà un'kɔɔn anà nde mpɛl sye awà ntɛɛn. Nde mpɛl kan'kwo mutswà mɔ̈ɔ̈ anà mudwa wa. Ngye, ngye awà nà mutsüül mbääb angye mbar?
\s1 Làtön uyɔl
\p 
\v 13 Abun, bɛ baar làfàtɛn naa: « Ŋàbà, itàkal naa nkàswà, bi iyàkyà bul là. Bi kwo ikàkyer mbul mwɛy, bi isàkàtà an'yà, anà bi isàkàwal ngim. »
\v 14 Wɛɛ bɛ, bɛ làyöb anki akà ikikye naa nkàswà mɔ̈ɔ̈ abɛ asàkal aben, ntɔn bɛ làbà asànaa un'swey kan'mɛnà, ungö a kitaaŋ kan'fàyaalà.
\v 15 Le, bɛ làlàtɛn naa: « Isàkal naa Mwol kan'kwen, bi isàkal anà mɔ̈ɔ̈ anà bi isàkyer abà itàkal abunà. »
\v 16 Wɛɛ apanà bɛ làbàmuswaŋ ngaal unsà uyɔl abɛ. Uyɔl atubàbà bube.
\v 17 Abun, isàkal naa mbuur mwɛy akyàyöb mukyer ubwaŋ, wɛɛ isàkal naa nde ba ukyer anki, apan nde kan'bwà unsà man'be.
\c 5
\s1 Aŋun'naaŋ, ngyɛb akà bɛ!
\p 
\v 1 Abun, bɛ aŋun'naaŋ, làlel anà in'kwɛŋ, ntɔn mpay iyàyà udu a bɛ!
\v 2 Un'naaŋ abɛ wàŋàpɔɔn, ipfɛy abɛ in'swab myàkyàdyàdyà.
\v 3 Wɔl abɛ anà ngim abɛ yàŋàbwà an'tär, an'tär ama màsàlatɛɛl imbäl ibe, ma màsàdyà in'twaŋ abɛ asànaa mbaa. Bɛ làkyàköŋà in'naaŋ u ntsüü a taaŋ!
\v 4 Le, bɛ làkyàtɔn mufur baar bàfàsal uboo a an'ywaŋ abɛ. Làfur aba alà làmusà in'kwɛŋ, anà Nzam, Mwol aŋità, akyàwem in'tär a abweel abà.
\v 5 Mɔ̈ɔ̈ abɛ u mɛɛn kan'kal aŋàyɔl a indiir a ntwɛn anà un'sak. Ndür abɛ làkyàbuul may may asànaa ntsür adilà ilä mukyɛl un'kwaal.
\v 6 Bɛ làpɛ ntaaŋàmbar anà làdwä mbuur a balàbal. Nde in'peen kàlasi anki.
\s1 Nkääŋ a mpem
\p 
\v 7 Abun, atɔŋ, làkäl anà nkääŋ a mpem tii u ngyeel a Mwol. Làler un'lem a an'ywaŋ: nde afàdil imbɛŋ a mfun ifàtoo u mɛɛn ukɔɔn ayɔn tii mpal usàwal nde mbɛŋ atàtwɛb anà yàngöngö.
\v 8 Bɛ sye, làkäl anà nkääŋ a mpem. Làkäl anà mpem aŋàtsim ntɔn ngyeel a Mwol yà tsütsü.
\p 
\v 9 Atɔŋ, twon lan'kal anà buul u mpem bɛ a bɛ, ntɔn mutiin mukal kusà a làbay a nsaŋ. Le, ntɛɛn wà u mun a mbwo!
\v 10 Atɔŋ, unsà ndaa iler mpay anà nkääŋ a mpem, mbaan alab yà yà aŋangɔɔm abà bàtɛn kà ikɔb a Mwol.
\v 11 Làler: bi ifàkan aŋàmun'küünà. Bɛ làkyàwem làsaŋ a nkääŋ a mpem a Yɔb anà bɛ làkyàyöb ndaa kun'kyer Mwol, ntɔn Mwol wàŋàyɔl a mpem a ukwen anà ngyɛb.
\p 
\v 12 Wɛɛ unsà ya yanswà, atɔŋ amɛ, twon lan'dyà kyän itàkal u du, itàkal u mɛɛn, itàkal kà aben. Wɛy naa: « Inye » abɛ làkäl inye anà « Aay » abɛ làkäl aay, ntɔn bɛ làkɔɔn akwɛlà u mbar a Nzam.
\s1 Ngyamàkà ntɔn abɛy
\p 
\v 13 Nkye umwɛy uboo a bɛ wà unsà mpay? Wɛy nde uyamà. Nkye nde wà unsà un'sak? Wɛy nde utɔ̈l an'diim.
\v 14 Nkye wà anà mbuur uboo a bɛ awe anà ukyal? Wɛy nde ubel andweer a Ikööŋ, ntɔn ba bun'si u ngyamàkà, waa ungö bun'tsuul may udu a un'tswe ande kà ikↄb a Mwol.
\v 15 Ngyamàkà a làkwikilà isàkɔɔr un'bɛy, Mwol akyer asumbaar. Isàkal naa nde we anà man'be, bàkyerà asun'dwääl ma.
\v 16 Làkyey man'be abɛ bɛ a bɛ anà làyamà bɛ a bɛ, ntɔn bɛ làkɔɔrà. Ngyamàkà a mbuur a balàbal ifàsal ngwal mbɔɔn.
\v 17 Ɛli kàkäl mbuur asànaa bi, nde kàyamà unsà muküünà naa mbul ukɔ̈ɔ̈n anɔ, wa sye kànɔ̈ anki u mɛɛn isii a mbul tär a ngɔn syaam.
\v 18 Ungö, kàfàyamà nde, mbul kàkyer anɔ, mɛɛn màtwey imbɛŋ ama.
\p 
\v 19 Atɔŋ amɛ, isàkal naa umwɛy uboo a bɛ wàŋàbwà ndwaŋ, ukwɛl anà ndandaa, wɛɛ mbuur asin kàmun'fuur,
\v 20 làyöb naa ufuur mbuur a man'be u mbwo kàwɛy nde, yà mutswà mɔ̈ɔ̈ ande kà ukwà, anà mubiiŋ un'kàbɔ a man'be.
